{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6ecdf97d74","title":"在中共中央政治局常委扩大会议上的讲话（摘要）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da02fd316b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":16,"articleId":"6ecdf97d74"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"048d649ef9","type":"title","text":"在中共中央政治局常委扩大会议上的讲话（摘要）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"},{"id":"1e9cb74474","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的干部十几年来有些人变质了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"},{"id":"e49036f5f3","type":"paragraph","text":"左派群众起来夺权，这是好的。石派夺权当然不好。左派的力量发展很快。上海的左派工人去年十一月上句只有一千多人，今年一月上句一百万，再加上学生，就是主力。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"},{"id":"67598562f4","type":"paragraph","text":"过去是军队打江山，现在是工农自己打江山，军队帮助","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"},{"id":"b4a90f87ae","type":"paragraph","text":"群众选举新的干部，就让他们选嘛！厂长、书记让他们去选。被接管的地方可以选。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"},{"id":"3df70c687f","type":"paragraph","text":"接管很好，只管政务，不管业务，事情还是原来的人去搞，我们只管监督。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74"}],"page":{"id":"5c6f5ad108","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6ecdf97d74","start":273,"end":273}}}},"__N_SSG":true}